responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "49AEBAC14AFD39EA6E04F2AA5DF5B0E4", "Uulorian the Lost? The rumors are true, a mad mage has united the bandits. With their aid he hopes to claim not only Lionhold, but the portal to Sanctus! They believe him to be a mage returned from the realm of the dead. I would wager that he is instead a charlatain from Sanctus hoping to start his own empire.")
